[21/01/2019 03:10:53] <font color="#ffff00">El Ciro, Jartum, Kuala Lampur,</font>
[21/01/2019 03:10:53] <font color="#ffff00">Manila, Hai Phong y Bangkok.</font>
[21/01/2019 03:10:57] <font color="#ffff00">No obstante, el destino final</font>
